MinecraftBot is a simple bot meant to integrate IRC and Minecraft chat.
It uses the PircBotX library (http://code.google.com/p/pircbotx/) to connect to and interact with IRC.

More info
-Bukkit forums: http://forums.bukkit.org/threads/65448/
-BukkitDev: http://dev.bukkit.org/server-mods/irc-minecraftbot/
